"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-29-frances-leon-marchand-wins-mens-olympic-400m-medley-gold\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - Leon Marchand surged to France's first Olympic swimming gold since 2012 on Sunday, obliterating the field to clock the second-fastest 400m individual medley time ever.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5584454732874391, \"rank\": 0.7730956546945671, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 46, \"end\": 52, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5584454732874391, \"rank\": 0.7730956546945671, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old led off strongly and never looked back, touching in 4mins 02.95secs, nearly six seconds clear of Japan's Tomoyuki Matsushita in second, with American Carson Foster third.\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 304, \"end\": 309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.9792226100376841, \"rank\": 0.02011224484102932, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 321, \"end\": 331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panasonic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.258756358920528e-13, \"text\": \"Matsushita\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panasonic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panasonic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marchand was heavy favourite after demolishing Michael Phelps' 15-year-old world record in a phenomenal 4:02.50 swim last year.\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.300922888306037e-50, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His performance at a raucous La Defense Arena in Paris was a new Olympic record.\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 557, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999993082838, \"rank\": 6.917114723489699e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With American defending champion Chase Kalisz failing to reach the final and with the packed crowd roaring him on, Marchand was half a body length clear after the opening butterfly leg.\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997921117420724, \"rank\": 0.00016597400150743553, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 623, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chase_Kalisz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chase Kalisz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chase_Kalisz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chase_Kalisz\"}, {\"begin\": 705, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999977893386919, \"rank\": 1.2225604878422373e-06, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was a sensational backstroke 100m that left his rivals trailing.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Trained by Phelps's old coach, Bob Bowman, his win made him France's first pool gold medallist since the London Games, when they won four.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 861, \"end\": 867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.999998711422825, \"rank\": 1.28829698372581e-06, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 881, \"end\": 884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"score\": 0.9999541131197516, \"rank\": 4.4216796453885684e-05, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\"}, {\"begin\": 885, \"end\": 891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"score\": 0.999998709611796, \"rank\": 6.80499514389672e-07, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the 2021 Olympics, they took home just one swimming medal, Florent Manaudou's silver from the 50m free.\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florent_Manaudou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.900645418367378e-29, \"text\": \"Florent\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florent_Manaudou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florent_Manaudou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marchand, a five-time world champion, will also swim the 200m medley and 200m butterfly as he builds on his burgeoning reputation.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": []}]}"